_sText:
It's one of my first maps. The map name explains everything. It's not big office, so the action is very fast. CT cant camp, they must hurry to get upstairs. T must quickly take the positions to defend themselves. Map is not done yet - it has a few bugs (like black wall at the office entry). But it's very detailed. 

I hope you like it!

Please, leave the comment ;)
